derlabs.com/)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/1GcjF4kcSt0SXgK5xTEt9.png?height=847&width=1732)\\n\\n[Stader](https://staderlabs.com/) is a non-custodial smart contract based staking platform that helps you conveniently discover and access staking solutions\\n\\n7/\\n\\n[@indexcoop](https://twitter.com/indexcoop) [$DPI](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24DPI&src=cashtag_click) December rebalance is live\\n\\n[@ApertureFinance](https://twitter.com/ApertureFinance) private beta coming in January\\n\\n# Cross-chain Investment Made Easy\\n\\nWith integrated bridge solutions Aperture is your gateway to DeFi 2.0.\\n\\n[网址](https://aperture.finance/)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/byEc6jT_z2lWDSCvUY2n8.png?height=946&width=1820)\\n\\n[@futureswapx](https://twitter.com/futureswapx) hosts 5th community call\\n\\n[https://www.futureswap.com/](https://www.futureswap.com/)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/JfIdcq8vigFOYKy0i2HZI.png?height=895&width=1670)\\n\\n[BUILT ON ETH. POWERED BY YOU.](https://www.futureswap.com/)\\n\\n# The Future of Perpetuals Is Here\\n\\nLeverage on any tokens with a protocol trusted with billions for its price execution, super low fees and reliability.\\n\\n[@QiDaoProtocol](https://twitter.com/QiDaoProtocol) and [@fraxfinance](https://twitter.com/fraxfinance) partner\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/vauWtf1QRhPMmuzPKOBvU.png?height=983&width=1586)\\n\\n## Zero-interest crypto lending - making DeFi accessible for all\\n\\n[Mai Finance i](https://www.mai.finance/)s a way for you to keep your crypto and still be able to spend its value. That means you're able to borrow stablecoins without having to sell your crypto assets, and do so at 0% interest.\\n\\nThe process is simple: create a vault, deposit your crypto assets, and start borrowing stablecoins against your collateral’s value.\\n\\nMai Finance is a website that connects users to the QiDao Protocol, which is where the vaults are created and stablecoins are borrowed.\\n\\n[@jaspermalamud](https://twitter.com/jaspermalamud) teases mobile NFT notifications in [@zapper_fi](https://twitter.com/zapper_fi)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/09v7rBU7uwpQs0JoIgesb.png?height=912&width=1696)\\n\\n8/\\n\\n[@epnsproject](https://twitter.com/epnsproject) releases 2021 Year in Reivew\\n\\n[@MinaProtocol](https://twitter.com/MinaProtocol) Mina Foundation Annual Report is live\\n\\n# The world's lightest blockchain, powered by participants.\\n\\n## Mina is building a gateway between the real world and crypto — and the infrastructure for the secure, democratic future we all deserve.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_NI3o_mmW7VksoN0ixLcA.png?height=930&width=1878)\\n\\n[http://minaprotocol.com/wp-content/uploads/MinaFoundation_TransparencyReport_2021.pdf](http://minaprotocol.com/wp-content/uploads/MinaFoundation_TransparencyReport_2021.pdf)\\n\\n[@prometheusdao](https://twitter.com/prometheusdao) announces  [@reflexerfinance](https://twitter.com/reflexerfinance) Bond Integration\\n\\nMMORPG-based decentralized reserve currency on Polygon. Probably nothing.\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/prometheusdao/status/1478179103027212291](https://twitter.com/prometheusdao/status/1478179103027212291)\\n\\n[@iearnfinance](https://twitter.com/iearnfinance) drops Yearn Finance Newsletter #52\\n\\n[@YamFinance](https://twitter.com/YamFinance) asks for feedback on purchasing CRV/CVX to Mine Bribe Rewards\\n\\n[https://synths.yam.xyz/](https://synths.yam.xyz/)\\n\\n9/\\n\\n[@TheDaoMaker](https://twitter.com/TheDaoMaker) was whitelisted on[@Bancor](https://twitter.com/Bancor)\\n\\n[@snx_weave](https://twitter.com/snx_weave) releases SNXweave Weekly Recap\\n\\n# SNXweave\\n\\nBy SNX Weave\\n\\nSNXweave is a grantsDAO initiative to improve communication and transparency across the Synthetix ecosystem. This podcast will give quick weekly recaps of n